# Netlify CORS Proxy — rewrites /cf-api/* and /sms-api/* to upstream APIs
# Matches instalarProxy() URL rewriting patterns (RECON.md §2.5, lines 1473-1484)
# Local dev: instalarProxy() skips on file:// protocol. Use Netlify CLI (netlify dev) for local proxy.

/cf-api/*  https://api.cloudflare.com/:splat  200
/sms-api/* https://api.sms24h.org/:splat  200
/sms-api/* https://sms24h.org/:splat  200
